summary:
I am a young architect from Fabriano in Italy, willing to put into practice the knowledge acquired during university studies and working experience. Hardworking and interested in growing personally and professionally, used to working constantly and meticulously. 
I think the secret ambition of architecture is to become invisible, to be taken up into the culture, absorbed into the background.
